      "@type": "del:Argument",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_argument_587fa1c2-9118-4d1a-a14e-3dbe42e3c147",
      "del:text": "'That makes sense , but I think that''s the point of this exercise is to get us talking about his specifically'"
